WEBVTT

00:02:28.480 --> 00:02:31.456
We stopped seeing
something in plain sight.

00:02:31.480 --> 00:02:36.616
We began to think of milk as standardized,
homogenized, pasteurized,

00:02:36.640 --> 00:02:39.600
packaged, powdered,
flavored and formulated.

00:02:40.680 --> 00:02:42.856
We abandoned the milk of human kindness

00:02:42.880 --> 00:02:44.920
and turned our priorities elsewhere.

00:02:46.560 --> 00:02:48.296
At the National Institutes of Health

00:02:48.320 --> 00:02:49.936
in Washington DC

00:02:49.960 --> 00:02:51.800
is the National Library of Medicine,

00:02:52.520 --> 00:02:55.256
which contains 25 million articles --

00:02:55.280 --> 00:02:59.520
the brain trust of life science
and biomedical research.